{"tid":1701413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中環千人快閃 罵退警員","createTime":"2019-11-09T04:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T05:11:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"102ce53ce5dc32ec9b0d2da6cdabd7b88b2bdef5","tid":1701413,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:58:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191109/ZLSOOXBFYXWSCDMRAW2KYKB7LY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191109%2FZLSOOXBFYXWSCDMRAW2KYKB7LY%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=24f97fc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191109%2FZLSOOXBFYXWSCDMRAW2KYKB7LY%2F&h=cf701f95\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191109/ZLSOOXBFYXWSCDMRAW2KYKB7LY/</a><br />\n<br />\n中環千人快閃 罵退警員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】周梓樂死訊早上傳出後，多區有群眾自發悼念，其中午膳時間中環有逾千人佔據德輔道中遊行，部份參加者情緒激憤，有人哽咽落淚，高呼「香港人，報仇」等口號。有人堵塞畢打街十字路口兩小時抗議，警方表現罕有克制，未有武力清場。<br />\n<br />\n過千人中午12時半響應網民號召，到中環遮打花園快閃集會悼念周梓樂。警員到場舉黃旗，集會人士齊聲指罵「殺人犯」，警員最後撤走。各人先默哀，有人不禁拭淚。其後他們走出德輔道中，舉起「魔警橫行亂殺人」黑色直幡遊行，途中不斷高喊「追究警暴，血債血償」等口號，不少身穿西裝的上班族加入，人數增至逾千人，電車乘客、天橋上行人亦高舉手掌表示支持。隊伍到前中環街市折返，在畢打街的十字路口再默哀一分鐘。不少人激動落淚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/vJ57DiOV3RQ-c37b8CCSjHkmu1w=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/H2XQIU7GNE6BRZCNVTJYLUANJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FvJ57DiOV3RQ-c37b8CCSjHkmu1w%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FH2XQIU7GNE6BRZCNVTJYLUANJY.jpg&h=aeeae75f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中環昨有逾千人走出馬路快閃遊行，悼念周梓樂。董立華攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中學生遭警掩口押走<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：畢業禮接噩耗 科大生洶湧<br />\n<br />\n隊伍走回遮打花園，有蒙面參加者呼籲和理非行多一步對抗警暴，參與罷工，「唔好當香港人報仇只係一句口號！」有戴V煞面具的黑衣參加者表示，反修例運動開始至今的多宗自殺案件都有可疑，而指周梓樂是失足墮樓更令人難以置信。他指港人不應害怕，「我哋冇退縮餘地，雨傘已輸了一次，退縮就會輸埋第二次，再輸已經係玩完」。<br />\n<br />\n遊行結束後，百多人不肯離開，由下午1時半起用雜物堵塞畢打街十字路口，中環交通非常擠塞，多輛警車泊在干諾道中戒備。到下午3時，多名軍裝警員到場呼籲市民返回行人路及疏導交通。警員指稱市民已堵路兩小時，警方已盡量容忍，「知道大家好唔開心，我哋都好唔開心」。<br />\n<br />\n現場人士不斷指罵「黑警」、「做咁多陰騭嘢」。警員未有如以往般武力對付，其後更收隊離開。下午3時45分，有人又嘗試用雪糕筒堵路，警方趕到，追入中環站，以「公眾地方行為不檢」罪名拘捕一名中學生，他欲回答旁觀途人問題時，被警員用手掩口押上警車，防暴警亦到場在畢打街一帶巡邏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/CuI9RWiSlMVjWbNLwL9hHrLNzCo=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/YTF7OX2AMICELELPKH72S2HZCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FCuI9RWiSlMVjWbNLwL9hHrLNzCo%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FYTF7OX2AMICELELPKH72S2HZCA.jpg&h=f8afac5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員在中環站拘捕一名中學生，並強行掩口禁止回答途人問題。<br />\nAppleDaily"},{"pid":"afd8fef7db3134ac1780a727b452a19fc41f3ae3","tid":1701413,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:05:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">出門前入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\n（最新）Senator Rubio 出聲講議員被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=b6daadac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&h=d2de161b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846</a><br />\n仲有Senator Rubio都知道周同學死訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=29544adb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&h=c4dc6427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n（最新）Senator Scott 都出聲講議員被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006%3Fs%3D19&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=490acf4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006%3Fs%3D19&h=01c0cece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n（突發）Senator Hawley 同 Solomon Yue 知道議員被拉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a0493f02c47905c23b707e787cd75255b579b75d","tid":1701413,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:08:03.000Z","msg":"捂口都得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a2472d42aeb7cab2fa2d448420b4efba5b5689","tid":1701413,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:11:05.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子當街擄走人質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />簡直無法無天"},{"pid":"155a6fb21638d5148dcc77b798523cb90a55a25a","tid":1701413,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}